comments: I was able to donate the shape from the first part of each word by the end, but I had trouble remembering the variations of the spellings.  I also did not notice the patterns for the different suffixes, presuming there was some kind of pattern that I was missing (it seemed to be tied to the colours).  I did not make any notes as everything went by quickly and I felt it would be against the spirit of the game.  Overall, I enjoyed it, but perhaps more time spent at the beginning on learning the formula would be more beneficial.
